vg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xqq1665702735396.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xqq1665702735396.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xqq1665702735396.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xqq1665702735396\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      widetable overflow\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets the length of overflow table segments to 8000 characters.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xqq1665702735396__topic_d60194e1_d60195e1_d60196e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xqq1665702735396__p_d60197e1_d60198e1_d60199e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= widetable overflow</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xqq1665702735396__section_d5s_dyw_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d889103e63\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xqq1665702735396__p_d60203e1_d60204e1_d60205e1\">The maximum field length is 8000 characters. Normally\n            the maximum field length and the overflow segment size would be expected to be the same.\n            However, for backward compatibility with databases created with earlier Sybase\n            connectors, the default segment size of overflow tables is 255 characters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xqq1665702735396__p_d60206e1_d60207e1_d60208e1\">You can use this option to increase the overflow\n            segment size from the default 255 characters to 8000 characters.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/taw1665702969612.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Table Management on Sybase</a><p>The Sybase connector maps Uniface entities to Sybase tables. When Uniface entities are created on the fly or via the Create Table facility, a Sybase table, its indexes, and a group of stored procedures are also created. The connector can also be used to map Uniface entities to Sybase views.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533856\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533856\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "widetable overflow Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 widetable overflow Sets the length of overflow table segments to 8000 characters. USYS$SYB_PARAMS = widetable overflow Description The maximum field length is 8000 characters. Normally the maximum field length and the overflow segment size would be expected to be the same. However, for backward compatibility with databases created with earlier Sybase connectors, the default segment size of overflow tables is 255 characters. You can use this option to increase the overflow segment size from the default 255 characters to 8000 characters. Related Links Table Management on Sybase The Sybase connector maps Uniface entities to Sybase tables. When Uniface entities are created on the fly or via the Create Table facility, a Sybase table, its indexes, and a group of stored procedures are also created. The connector can also be used to map Uniface entities to Sybase views. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}